42 different possible shape positions/flips etc

42^8 (9682651996416) maximum possible combinations

technically it's less... it's 42*(some reduced value)* etc. where we take away each possible shape combinations. i'm too lazy to write that out

advantage of being as soon as a shape doesn't fit, we can skip all other combinations of shapes in other positions.













